hardcoded List the model loader modules that Panda will automatically import
when a new, unknown model type is loaded. This may be either the name of
a module, or a space-separate list of filename extensions, followed by
the name of the module. load-video-type list * p3ffmpeg (from Confauto.prc); hardcoded List the video loader modules that Panda will automatically import
when a new, unknown video type is loaded. This may be either the name of
a module, or a space-separate list of filename extensions, followed by
the name of the module. loader-num-threads int 1 The number of threads that will be started by the Loader class to
load models asynchronously. These threads will only be started if the
asynchronous interface is used, and if threading support is compiled
